{
  "stem": "1530.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They have two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They have Hannah, who is five years old, brilliant and gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's Benjamin, who is out of this world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never heard anybody so bright in my life-- and gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I have trouble.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have trouble with Yolanda because I am still so involved in my hurt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It doesn't want to leave me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No matter how much therapy I had, for 45 years, it's there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'd love to get rid of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But, I mean, I'm too old already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have to learn and live with my, my-- I'm a crippled person, I feel of myself as such.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even though in-between, you know, I, I designed clothes and I sold it on Madison Avenue, and I, I think I'm somewhat of a decorator, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did beautiful things, and we traveled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I must have given a lot of things to my husband because he wouldn't have stayed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I still feel like a victim, even though-- I mean, I have-- I always say this to people because they look at me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I say, yes, I have everything in life-- a loving husband, children, grandchildren, my son-in-law.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't have [SOBBING] myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SOBBING] I don't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not trying to impress what-- I've been left, I think, a little more crippled than some other people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is my feeling about myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it's a difficult life, even though I have everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now I'm getting older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what happens in life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Things become more exaggerated as you get older.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm-- I'd like to come to some terms, definitely, with my daughter, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That I-- I just couldn't tell her anything about Auschwitz when she was growing up.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
